Package com.example.lotteryevent.viewmodels

Class UserProfileViewModel

java.lang.Object
androidx.lifecycle.ViewModel
com.example.lotteryevent.viewmodels.UserProfileViewModel
public class UserProfileViewModel extends androidx.lifecycle.ViewModel
ViewModel for the UserProfile screen, responsible for preparing and managing the data for the UI

This ViewModel provides the UserProfileFragment with the necessary data, such as the currently active user, loading status, and error messages. It acts as an intermediary between the UI and the data layer (represented by IUserRepository

This class is decoupled from the data source implementation, communicating only with the user repository interface.
